Key Match Events: Chancel Mbemba scored in the 27th minute
Yoane Wissa scored in the 65th minute (penalty)
Arthur Masuaku scored in the 82nd minute
Mohamed Bayo scored a penalty for Guinea in the 21st minute
Post-Match Reflections: Congo DR came from behind to beat Guinea 3-1
Congo DR will join Nigeria in the AFCON semifinals
Miscellaneous Highlights: The match took place at the Alassane Ouattara Olympic Stadium in Abidjan, Ivory Coast
